<Layout::Text text-l text-f>
	<h3><code>LET</code></h3>
	<Code @name="docs-surrealql-statements-let-syntax.typescript" text="SQL Syntax">
		LET $@parameter = @value;
	</Code>
	<p>The following query shows example usage of this statement:</p>
	<Code @name="docs-surrealql-statements-let-simple.sql">
		LET $param = "some value";
	</Code>
</Layout::Text>

